metadata.name: The Flying Fortress of Ba'zar Alkar
metadata.description:
Denizens of the Marshlands are delighted to have the everlasting presence of Ba'zar Alkar, the finest alchemist and machinist throughout all eighteen Great Lakes. 

His Flying fortress, made to resemble his feline friend, Maggie, serves as both his humble abode, and a surprisingly efficient way of transportation. 

"That Damn Fortress of Ba'zar, can a man get some sleep?"
